        <item>
            <title>劉德華現身華為 Mate XT 非凡大師宣傳片　全球首個三摺疊手機登場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-matext-andylau</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[劉德華]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[華為]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260993</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">華為今日正式發布非凡大師品牌全新三摺疊式手機 Mate XT 宣傳片，品牌大使劉德華更出現在宣傳片中並手持 Mate XT 為其首次公開真身。Mate XT 是全球首個三摺疊式手機，預料會是 9 月 10 日舉行「華為見非凡品牌盛典及鴻蒙智行新品發布會」的主角。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_30407"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nG47VNO9ySE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">Mate XT 採用了「內折 + 外折 + 雙鉸鏈」的設計，從宣傳片中可以看到 Mate XT 完全展開後的屏幕非常巨大，大約為 10 吋。Mate XT 在厚度控制上的表現同樣相當出色，展開後的屏幕厚度預計不超過 5 mm。手機的背部與 Mate 60 RS 非凡大師相似，採用了八角形的鏡頭模組，當中還有一個方形的潛望式長焦鏡頭。背部使用了素皮材質，底部印有華為和 ULTIMATE DESIGN（非凡大師）品牌的標誌。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261044 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img-694x298.jpg" alt="Mate XT" width="694" height="298" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img-694x298.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261042 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign-694x390.jpg" alt="Mate XT" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.huaweicentral.com/here-is-the-first-official-look-at-huawei-mate-xt-tri-fold-phone/">Huawei Central</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">華為常務董事兼終端 BG 董事長餘承東早前表示華為接下來推出的這一代摺疊式手機，是別人想得到但做不到的產品。華為團隊為了 Mate XT 概念的構想已長達 5 年有多，如今終於可以量產並面世。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/1839167003?luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1005051839167003">微博 @華為終端</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/11/huawei-matebook-x-pro-review-2/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Huawei MateBook X Pro　外形　手感　屏幕　鍵盤　功能　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/04/stability-issues-hold-back-huawei-ai-chips-to-outpace-nvidia-report/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為 AI 晶片難取代 Nvidia　中國企業指 Ascend 晶片不穩定又慢</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為撞 Apple 於同一日舉行發布會，餘承東：將發布華為巔峯之作</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/">劉德華現身華為 Mate XT 非凡大師宣傳片　全球首個三摺疊手機登場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
