        <item>
            <title>淘寶天貓將支援微信支付   9 月陸續分批開放用户使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=taobao-wechatpay</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[買物情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wechat pay]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[淘寶]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260962</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">淘寶早在年初便已經有用户發現，部分淘寶訂單的支付頁面出現「微信支付」的選項，可以轉至「微信支付」進行付款。當時已經有淘寶計劃全面支援「微信支付」服務的消息。最近淘寶和天貓分別發出公告計劃新增「微信支付」服務，目前已向部分商家發出邀請試用，簽約後即可開通「微信支付」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260968 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355-694x307.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="307" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355-694x307.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260972 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123-694x433.jpg" alt="淘寶" width="694" height="433" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123-694x433.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://helpcenter.taobao.com/servicehall/knowledge_detail?kwdContentId=543618262673589248&amp;spm=service_hall.25034535.shcLibrary_lcork9x3.543618262673589248&amp;hcSessionId=3-1281-fa798edf-2618-47b4-b845-27acacb81bfe#1000113210,1000113484,,">淘寶</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">阿里巴巴旗下淘寶和天貓發出意見徵集，指為提升消費者的購物體驗正計劃新增「微信支付」服務。目前淘寶已經向部分商家發出試用的邀請，而在淘寶的商家服務大廳中也能發現「微信支付」的一系列使用指南。商家簽約完成開通「微信支付」服務後，消費者在對應的店舖便能使用「微信支付」進行付款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260975 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812-325x580.jpeg" alt="" width="325" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812-325x580.jpeg 325w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812.jpeg 364w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 325px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://helpcenter.taobao.com/servicehall/knowledge_detail?kwdContentId=543618262673589248&amp;spm=service_hall.25034535.shcLibrary_lcork9x3.543618262673589248&amp;hcSessionId=3-1281-fa798edf-2618-47b4-b845-27acacb81bfe#1000113210,1000113484,,">淘寶</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">淘寶表示目前「微信支付」服務僅向部分商家發出邀請，而未有收到邀請的商家亦無需焦急，預料 9 月中旬會分批給更多商家加入開通「微信支付」服務的計劃。其實一直有淘寶開通「微信支付」的呼聲，其競爭對手「拼多多」很早之前便已經有「微信支付」的服務，早前市值更一度超越阿里巴巴。如今淘寶開通「微信支付」相信有助改善購物體驗，方便用户的使用同樣能吸引更多新用户，增強競爭力。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://app.xinhuanet.com/news/article.html?articleId=a811ef63-298b-4185-8806-282dc65ccebf&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawFGC3FleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHaXbXGCcVbI0J_bHfR3HMwpkNj_7BlTFocuXhpmGcxK-F9YdfrpXSmFbbw_aem_uM3myJE8KJLRCInt3cMS-w">新華網</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.cbndata.com/information/222386">CBNData</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/taobao-xiaomi-vision-pro-trial-su7-car/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">安坐家中 Vision Pro 雲端試車　淘寶小米合作推虛擬小米 SU7 試車體驗</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/octopus-wechatpayhk-taxi/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">香港的士增設微信支付，加入至八達通支付網絡</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/taobao-campaign-free-delivery-worldwide/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">淘寶推全球包郵計劃，港澳台等亞洲地區率先提供</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/">淘寶天貓將支援微信支付   9 月陸續分批開放用户使用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
